icer at Auschwitz concentration camp executed for war crimes\n\n==Twin towns \u2014 sister cities==\n{{See also|List of twin towns and sister cities in the Czech Republic}}\n\nBolatice is [[Twin towns and sister cities|twinned]] with:<ref>{{cite web |title=Partnersk\u00e9 obce|url=http://www.bolatice.cz/obec-bolatice/rozvoj-a-strategie/partnerske-obce/|publisher=Obec Bolatice|language=cs|accessdate=2019-08-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Do Slan\u00e9ho p\u0159ijeli host\u00e9 z partnersk\u00fdch m\u011bst|url=http://meuslany.cz/vismo/dokumenty2.asp?id_org=14936&id=61723&n=do%2Dslaneho%2Dprijeli%2Dhoste%2Dz%2Dpartnerskych%2Dmest|publisher=M\u011bsto Slan\u00fd|language=cs|date=2017-10-04|accessdate=2019-08-24}}</ref>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|SVK}} [[Do\u013eany, Pezinok District|Do\u013eany]], [[Slovakia]]\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Linum (village)|Linum]], [[Germany]]\n*{{flagicon|HUN}} [[Nagykov\u00e1csi]], [[Hungary]]\n*{{flagicon|POL}} [[Rudy, Silesian Voivodeship|Rudy]], [[Poland]]\n*{{flagicon|CZE}} [[Slan\u00fd]], [[\u010cesko]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.bolatice.cz Official website]\n\n{{commons category|Bolatice}}\n{{Opava District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Opava District]]\n[[Category:Hlu\u010d\u00edn Region]]\n\n\n{{MoraviaSilesia-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Bolatice\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=Bolatice, kostel sv. Stanislava 6.JPG\n|image_caption=St. Stanislaus Church in Bolatice\n|image_shield=CoA_of_Bolatice.svg\n|image_flag=Flag_of_Bolatice.svg\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[Moravian-Silesian Region|Moravian-Silesian]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Opava District|Opava]]\n|leader_title            = Mayor\n|leader_name             = Herbert Pavera\n|